OL,6,F"In my opinion, which is formed with
OL,7,Fthe assistance of psychiatric reports,
OL,8,Fyou continue to pose a very real and
OL,9,Fsignificant danger to the public of
OL,10,Fserious harm from future violent
OL,11,Foffences."
OL,13,FThe court heard Moore believed that he
OL,14,Fwas being stalked by a man he believed
OL,15,Fto be a former work colleague and that
OL,16,FMr Mayo was involved in the conspiracy
OL,17,Fagainst him.
