OL,6,F"It is patently clear that Mr Mayo is
OL,7,Fa man who will be very much missed,"
OL,8,Fhe added.
OL,10,FCatherine Spedding, representing
OL,11,FMoore, said her client had worked as a
OL,12,Fsoftware engineer and had no previous
OL,13,Fconvictions or history of mental
OL,14,Fhealth concerns.
OL,16,F"He says he very much regrets his
OL,17,Factions," she added.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
