OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Wayne Usher,
OL,7,Fof Gloucestershire Police, said: "This
OL,8,Fwas a horrific and sustained attack on
OL,9,Fa defenceless man that has had a
OL,10,Fdevastating impact on the family.
OL,12,F"This sentence allows Moore to be
OL,13,Fdetained indefinitely in an
OL,14,Fappropriate institution where he can
OL,15,Freceive the support he needs."
